## Note : my Notmuch configuration set the tag "new" to all new message.

+acmontpellier -- tag:new AND (DeliveredTo:@ac-montpellier.fr OR to:/@ac-montpellier.fr/ OR from:/@ac-montpellier.fr/ OR cc:/@ac-montpellier.fr/ OR bcc:/@ac-montpellier.fr/)
+inbox -- tag:new AND 'folder:"acmontpellier/inbox"'
-unread -inbox -delete +deleted -- 'folder:"acmontpellier/trash"'
-unread -inbox +sent -- 'folder:"acmontpellier/sent"'
